---
layout: base
title: Site Changelog
description: A record of features, sections, and projects added to The Freethinking Times over time.
permalink: /changelog/
---

<div class="container changelog-page">

  <header class="changelog-page__header">
    <h1 class="changelog-page__title">Changelog</h1>
    <p class="changelog-page__lede">What has been built, when, and why. This publication is an ongoing project, readers who care about it deserve to see it develop.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="changelog-timeline">
    {% for entry in changelog %}
    <div class="changelog-entry">

      <div class="changelog-entry__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="changelog-entry__content">
        <div class="changelog-entry__meta">
          <time class="changelog-entry__date" datetime="{{ entry.date }}">
            {{ entry.date | readableDate }}
          </time>
          <h2 class="changelog-entry__title">{{ entry.title }}</h2>
        </div>

        {% if entry.sections %}
          {% for section in entry.sections %}
          <div class="changelog-section">
            <p class="changelog-section__label">{{ section.label }}</p>
            <ul class="changelog-list">
              {% for item in section.entries %}
              <li class="changelog-list__item">{{ item }}</li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        {% else %}
          <ul class="changelog-list">
            {% for item in entry.entries %}
            <li class="changelog-list__item">{{ item }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% endif %}

      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</div>
